  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Starting at 14th level, you gain the ability to align your consciousness to the endless calculations of Mechanus. As a bonus action, you can enter this state for 1 minute. For the duration, attack rolls against you can't benefit from <strong>advantage</strong>, and whenever you make an attack roll, an ability check, or a saving throw, you can treat a roll of <strong>9 or lower</strong> on the d20 as a <strong>10</strong>.</p><p>Once you use this bonus action, you can't use it again until you finish a <strong>long rest</strong>, unless you spend 5 @UUID[Compendium.5e-complete.5e-class-features.7hAcETWHOVguR2ZF]{Sorcery Points} to use it again.</p>",
